sentence: Is EECS 376 essential to my graduation ?
sentence-with-vars: Is department0 number0 essential to my graduation ?
sql: SELECT COUNT( COURSEalias0.NUMBER ) , COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT , COURSEalias0.NUMBER FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 , PROGRAM_COURSE AS PROGRAM_COURSEalias0 WHERE COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT = "EECS" AND COURSEalias0.NUMBER = 376 AND PROGRAM_COURSEalias0.CATEGORY = "Core" AND PROGRAM_COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID ;
